										></span>
									</div>
								))}
							</div>
						</div>

						<p class="weights-note">
							Training repeatedly tunes the weights so this equation gets better at predicting useful next-token probability maps.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<hr class="rule" />

