						<li>Some useful world knowledge is stored in the network parameters.</li>
						<li>You can already build applications with clever prompts: few-shot translation, or a prompt that fakes an assistant conversation.</li>
						<li>But we can make the behavior much more useful.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
