						<h2 id="rlhf-title" class="promise">Reinforcement learning nudges the assistant toward preferred answers.</h2>
						<ul class="rlhf-list">
							<li>RLHF means Reinforcement Learning from Human Feedback.</li>
							<li>Humans rank multiple model outputs for the same prompt.</li>
							<li>Those rankings train a reward model to predict what humans prefer.</li>
							<li>The LLM is optimized against that reward model.</li>
							<li>It helps shape behavior more than raw knowledge: helpful, honest, harmless, concise, and polite.</li>
						</ul>
